## Map Customization Options

### Color & Style Settings

| Setting | Default | Description |
|---------|---------|-------------|
| Header background color | theme-dependent | Header area background |
| Header text color | theme-dependent | Header text color |
| Border color | theme-dependent | Card border color |
| Tsunami bar background | theme-dependent | Tsunami info area background |
| Tsunami bar text color | theme-dependent | Tsunami info text color |
| Marker color | theme-dependent | Epicenter marker color |
| Badge border color | theme-dependent | Intensity badge border |
| Frame accent color | theme-dependent | Frame color (kawaii theme) |
| Frame thickness | 100% | Frame width, kawaii theme (0–500%) |

### Size & Font Settings

| Setting | Default | Description |
|---------|---------|-------------|
| Font | zen-maru-gothic | 12 fonts (see below) |
| Marker size | 100% | Epicenter marker size |
| Label size | 100% | Prefecture label size |
| Header font size | 120% | Header text size |
| Tsunami font size | 160% | Tsunami info text size |
| Time font size | 120% | Time display size |
| Opacity | 90 | 0–100% |

### Display & Behavior Settings

| Setting | Default | Description |
|---------|---------|-------------|
| Auto zoom | ON | Auto-zoom to epicenter |
| Intensity coloring | ON | Color-code by seismic intensity |
| Intensity labels | ON | Prefecture intensity labels |
| Tsunami bar | ON | Show tsunami info bar |
| Header info | ON | Show header details |
| Sea transparency | ON | Transparent sea area |
| Display mode | timer | timer / always-on |
| Map display duration | 30 sec | 15–120 sec (timer mode) |

## Available Fonts

Both alert and map overlays support the following 12 fonts.

1. default
2. Zen Maru Gothic
3. Noto Sans JP
4. M PLUS Rounded 1c
5. Kosugi Maru
6. Kiwi Maru
7. Hachi Maru Pop
8. DotGothic16
9. Dela Gothic One
10. Shippori Mincho
11. Reggae One
12. Zen Antique

## Tips

- Changes are previewed in real-time on the Overlay Settings page
- Click Save to apply your changes, or Reset to revert to the theme defaults
- Each theme stores its own customization separately
